 2. the australian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person eating plum is the pakistani##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the colombian and the turkish##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the australian##1
10. the turkish is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the colombian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
